## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [nww]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Rootless phenotype. nww mutant embryos diverge from normal development at 32 cell stage. The  hypophysis asymmetric division fails resulting in loss of lens shaped cell. Consequently the quiescent center does not develop and roots are absent.
